"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     Data from: Shiroozu A, Okamura K, Ikenoue H, et al. Treatment of hyperthyroidism with a small single daily dose of methimazole.&nbsp;J Clin Endocrinol Metab 1986; 63:125.",
"    </div>",
"   </div>",
